Texts.Chs:
一罐金枪鱼。制作简单，但在大多数情况下是一个很好的蛋白质来源。它是在水中罐装的，而不像其他来源的油败坏它的味道。如果过量食用，会引发汞中毒。
^orange;类型：熟肉食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
A can of tuna. Simple, yet a great source of protein for the most part. This one is canned in water, as opposed to other oils that would affect its taste. Still a valid source of mercury poisoning if consumed in excess.
^orange;Type: Cooked Meat^reset;
